{"tid":1928180,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"伊斯蘭國呼籲聖戰士勿赴歐洲武漢肺炎疫區","createTime":"2020-03-16T08:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T10:20:50.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f98d2d7860012ed5886e2a7792c1ad53e266389b","tid":1928180,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:43:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3100781\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3100781&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=5edc1d25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3100781&h=6bed56ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3100781</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情險峻，歐洲多國也紛紛淪陷，義大利、西班牙等國接連宣布封鎖全境。對此，IS（伊斯蘭國）近來下達指令，要求其成員避免進入歐洲行動。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，過去數年來頻頻在歐洲發動恐怖攻擊的IS（The Islamic State），近來因應武漢肺炎疫情，正避開對歐洲各大城市的恐怖攻擊行動，更下令禁止成員「聖戰士」（jihadist）進入歐洲等疫區，以避免被感染病毒。<br />\n<br />\nIS發給其組織成員的通訊期刊「al-Naba」中刊載了IS所頒布的新版「伊斯蘭教條」（sharia directives）中，要求成員保持良好衛生習慣，例如在打哈欠與噴嚏時遮住口鼻，以及勤洗手。而在此之前，成員蒙面的慣例已行之有年，但主要是為了在斬首人質時，免於曝光身分，而非為了防疫。<br />\n<br />\nIS更要求，健康的成員不應進入歐洲，而已經染病的成員也不應試圖逃離，此命令被外界視為「聖戰」的一環，要求染病的「聖戰士」在當地擴大傳染。IS更稱，染上了病疫的人須承受疾病的折磨，而瘟疫是上天所降下的懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n而2月的「al-Naba」期刊，更將疫情歸咎於中國，並宣稱全能的神，因中國對維吾爾人進行大規模的迫害，而降下瘟疫於中國。<br />\n<br />\n伊斯蘭國在崩解後，其大部分的組織成員留於伊拉克。伊拉克至今累計確診已有110例，其中10例死亡。<br />\n<br />\nIS成員本月6日於阿富汗首都喀布爾發動恐怖攻擊活動，當局估計至少32人遭受槍擊死亡，81人受傷。"},{"pid":"3021da40f5bc8901f3603d33ad0f8d18e5a00b82","tid":1928180,"uid":3994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:44:11.000Z","msg":"勁過核武"},{"pid":"4ae717eefced032c130f1723cdb17f0aef0d8762","tid":1928180,"uid":522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:45:54.000Z","msg":"歐洲成功擊退伊斯蘭大軍"},{"pid":"3dcdab8dd00f84a52a509a1fd428fe8844cff486","tid":1928180,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:46:36.000Z","msg":"達爾文替身.jpg"},{"pid":"0dfa2e132cce2f33afb00a377cd85a910d33d657","tid":1928180,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:46:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而2月的「al-Naba」期刊，更將疫情歸咎於中國，並宣稱全能的神，因中國對維吾爾人進行大規模的迫害，而降下瘟疫於中國。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ddbe6f82498b018108d05428cbdadf5e687eb0","tid":1928180,"uid":48360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ae717eefced032c130f1723cdb17f0aef0d8762","tid":1928180,"uid":522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:45:54.000Z","msg":"歐洲成功擊退伊斯蘭大軍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:47:38.000Z","msg":"但難民呢?"},{"pid":"b0f19c92c1328885b0a63968bc5f65cd5abb69e4","tid":1928180,"uid":142965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:47:39.000Z","msg":"有膽搞自殺式襲擊冇膽去野肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ee428f6e39406cafcaaadc4318c24baf864df4","tid":1928180,"uid":103914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:47:54.000Z","msg":"去亞洲中國? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421a19795fac6f861b697c0a5f88c68310a3fe9f","tid":1928180,"uid":258342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:49:01.000Z","msg":"而2月的「al-Naba」期刊，更將疫情歸咎於中國，並宣稱全能的神，因中國對維吾爾人進行大規模的迫害，而降下瘟疫於中國。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a08289205ff55a82655e999e9f1efb92bbf96dcc","tid":1928180,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0f19c92c1328885b0a63968bc5f65cd5abb69e4","tid":1928180,"uid":142965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:47:39.000Z","msg":"有膽搞自殺式襲擊冇膽去野肺炎<img sr